      "writtenOn": "2021-06-29T21:51:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "stats.Handler is an interface, and I had to add the following check to stop unit tests panicking when `m.Logger \u003d\u003d nil` couldn\u0027t catch the nil correctly.\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/logdog/common/archive/archive.go;l\u003d104-106\n\nI thought the same applies?",
